<para>Signal statistics — sliding window min/max/mean/variance. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Maintains a circular buffer of samples and computes statistics incrementally. Designed for sensor data conditioning.</para>
<para>All math is integer-only. Mean and variance use Q16.16 for fractional precision without floating point.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">int32_t<sp/>samples[32];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structSYN__Signal" kindref="compound">SYN_Signal</ref><sp/>sig;</highlight></codeline>
